Class SelectFrom3Input

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jsyn.unitgen.UnitGenerator
      • fr.istic.groupimpl.synthesizer.vco.jsyn.SelectFrom3Input

  • public class SelectFrom3Input
extends com.jsyn.unitgen.UnitGenerator
    SelectUnit unit. Select Input1 or Input2 or Input3 based on value on inputSelect port. 
     output = switch inputSelects {
                case 1:  Input1
                case 2:  Input2
                case 3:  Input3
                default: Input1
            }
    Author:
    Team GroupImpl
